Job Opportunity for “AWS Engineer” @ Phoenix, AZ for 7 months contract

Dear Brian, 

I am impressed by your skills and experience, would like to present for “AWS Engineer” job opportunity at Phoenix, AZ. If you'd be interested in learning more about this. I would pass on your reference to my colleague Mr. Praveen Narava, "pnarava@lat36.com" / 510-256-7317, recruiting on this role (for his Direct Client – Blue Shield of California). He would be glad to send you a detailed job description and connect for expediting the submission. 

Looking forward to hearing from you soon with your contact details.

Thanks and have a great day.

Babu Tunk
Latitude 36 Inc - Resource Manager 
+1-716-240-0769
Why would blue shield California need DevOps in Phoenix?
Hi Brian, Please share your contact details here, will ask Praveen to give you a call and discuss the job opportunity. Thank you.
